description: Try our easy to follow Chicken Meatballs recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chicken Meatballs Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Mix together well with hands. Roll into small balls and place onto tray. Spray with oil and sprinkle over sesame seeds. Bake for 15-20 minutes or until golden and cooked through. Stand each meatball onto a slice of cucumber and top with a cherry tomato half. Secure with a toothpick. Serve.
